title: Berry Tart Recipe Demonstration - Joyofbaking.com
description:
Recipe here: http://www.joyofbaking.com/BerryTart.html Stephanie Jaworski of Joyofbaking.com demonstrates how to make a Freeform Berry Tart. This recipe is for a free form Berry Tart which is especially nice as it has a crisp and crumbly pastry base and the filling is made with a medley of lightly sweetened berries. Wonderful with scoop of vanilla ice cream or a dollop of softly whipped cream.
